      In Halo: Reach, players experience the fateful moments that 
      forged the Halo legend. It\'s the story of Noble Team, a squad 
      of heroic Spartan soldiers, and their final stand on planet 
      Reach, humanity\'s last line of defense between the terrifying 
      Covenant and Earth. This darker story is echoed by grittier 
      visuals amid a backdrop of massive, awe-inspiring environments. 
      Characters, enemies and environments are rendered in amazing 
      detail by an all-new engine designed to deliver epic-scale 
      encounters against the cunning and ruthless Covenant.

          Usage:
          For DevKit/JTAG hacked consoles ONLY!

          Copy to your USB/360HDD and boot via default.xex or create
          a NXE shorcut with Quickboot.  Files can also be burned as 
          data straight to disc, even a standard DVDR if size permits
          and bootable in same way as normal game.

          This is NOT a GOD game. This can be booted from any location
          and not just a 360HDD.  You can get exactly the same functionality
          as a GOD game simply by creating a NXE shortcut with QuickBoot.
